5Ô∏è‚É£ But how do I find partnerships Anon? Great question, there are 2 major ways that I consider the ‚Äúbest‚Äù. The first way is the POP method (Partners of Partners) in which you join one of our partner servers, and then join their partnered servers. Chances are almost none will be servers we have already partnered with. The second method is to go to https://disboard.org/servers/tag/politics and just look for servers there. If you have a different, better way of finding partners - by all means use that.

